<!-- Pricing FAQs -->
<section class="section-pad-sm bg-light">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-4">
      <span class="section-label">FAQs</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Pricing Questions</h2>
      <div class="section-divider mx-auto"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="row g-3 justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <div class="accordion accordion-flush" id="faqAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-item rounded mb-2" style="border:1px solid var(--border);">
            <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-bold" style="font-size:.9rem;" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq1">What is included in the hire rate?</button></h2>
            <div id="faq1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
              <div class="accordion-body text-muted" style="font-size:.88rem;">The hire rate covers use of the machine for the agreed period. Delivery, fuel (for diesel machines), and damage waiver are priced separately. All machines are delivered fully serviced and safety-checked.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-item rounded mb-2" style="border:1px solid var(--border);">
            <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-bold" style="font-size:.9rem;" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq2">Is there a minimum hire period?</button></h2>
            <div id="faq2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
              <div class="accordion-body text-muted" style="font-size:.88rem;">Our minimum hire period is one day. Weekly rates apply for 5-day hires, and we offer discounted 4-week rates for longer projects. Contact us for custom project pricing.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-item rounded mb-2" style="border:1px solid var(--border);">
            <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-bold" style="font-size:.9rem;" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq3">Do you deliver to my area?</button></h2>
            <div id="faq3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
              <div class="accordion-body text-muted" style="font-size:.88rem;">We primarily serve Auckland and the greater Auckland region. Delivery to Waikato, Northland, and other North Island locations can be arranged — please call us to discuss transport costs.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-item rounded mb-2" style="border:1px solid var(--border);">
            <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-bold" style="font-size:.9rem;" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq4">Do I need an operator's licence?</button></h2>
            <div id="faq4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
              <div class="accordion-body text-muted" style="font-size:.88rem;">No formal licence is required in NZ to operate a scissor lift or boom lift, but operators must be trained and competent as required under the Health and Safety at Work Act 2015. We can arrange training through our network of certified trainers on request.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-item rounded" style="border:1px solid var(--border);">
            <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-bold" style="font-size:.9rem;" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq5">Are prices GST inclusive?</button></h2>
            <div id="faq5" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
              <div class="accordion-body text-muted" style="font-size:.88rem;">All prices displayed are exclusive of GST. GST at the current NZ rate of 15% will be added to your invoice.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

